Copyright 2026 v810-hdl contributors

This product includes software developed as part of the v810-hdl project,
an open-source SystemVerilog implementation of the NEC V810 CPU.

This project is not affiliated with NEC Corporation. "V810" refers to the
publicly-documented NEC V810 family microprocessor architecture and is used
here solely to describe the subject of the implementation.

Reference emulators (MAME, Mednafen) were consulted as behavioral oracles
during development. No source code from those projects was copied into this
work; all HDL is independently authored from the NEC V810 family user manual
and related public specifications.
